Direct Known Subclasses:
ProjectionPredicate
public class FeaturePredicate<P,R>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Predicate<P>

This class provides a decorator predicate that applies a mapping to the arguments of the underlying predicate. Everytime arguments are passed to an invoke method of this class, the arguments are first mapped using a given mapping function and afterwards passed to the invoke method of the underlying predicate.
